2302	AFP_ENG_20080401.5035.LDC2009T13	Since Lance Gibbs ended his distinguished career on February 5, 1976, West Indies cricket history is littered with several bowlers plying the slow stuff that have been tossed aside in preference for bowlers living in the "fast lane".
