5153	APW_ENG_20070111.0227.LDC2009T13	Harris said conditions for prisoners are better because of the construction of Camp Five and, just last year, Camp Six -- steel- and-concrete buildings modeled after U.S. prisons.
5154	APW_ENG_20070111.0227.LDC2009T13	Human rights groups argue that the buildings, which have solid- wall one-person cells, leave the prisoners more isolated.
