5838	APW_ENG_20070202.1273.LDC2009T13	He offered a rousing promise to reverse Bush's policies.
5839	APW_ENG_20070202.1273.LDC2009T13	"Get the car out of the ditch, we aren't going to take fear for an answer any more in America," Dodd said, bringing the crowd of activists to its feet.
