5873	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	"We all agreed that Hamas has been trying for a long time to impose its control on the Gaza Strip, and Fatah needs to stand up to this policy of Hamas," said Amin Makboul, one of the group's members.
5874	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	However, participants disagreed over tactics and whether mediation efforts were useful, he said.
5875	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	In Gaza City, bursts of gunfire alternated with periods of calm.
5876	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	Thunderous shooting shook one beachside neighborhood for more than half an hour after nightfall Saturday, as Hamas gunmen fought a local clan allied with Abbas' security forces.
5877	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	The fighting continued early Sunday, with battles in nearly a dozen locations, including the headquarters of Preventive Security in Gaza City.
5878	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	In areas not affected by the fighting, people tried to go about their lives.
5879	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	Boys played soccer in the streets, horse-drawn carts maneuvered through alleys and shoppers stocked up on supplies for the next round of battle.
5880	APW_ENG_20070204.0494.LDC2009T13	In the Sheik Radwan neighborhood, Ali Ustaz used a lull to buy a battery-powered radio so he could follow developments despite frequent power cuts.
