6057	APW_ENG_20070220.1028.LDC2009T13	euro22.3 million) charge because of overstatements in income from its Nigerian operation.
6058	APW_ENG_20070220.1028.LDC2009T13	The accounting fraud was discovered in November, more than six months after Cadbury increased its stake in the operation from 46 percent to just over 50 percent.
