6114	APW_ENG_20070221.1497.LDC2009T13	The government lost the Senate motion by two votes, despite Foreign Minister Massimo D'Alema's calling for the coalition's forces -- which range from Christian Democrats to Communists -- to support Prodi's policies, including Italy's continued mission in Afghanistan.
6115	APW_ENG_20070221.1497.LDC2009T13	The Cabinet approved a decree for continued funding of the Afghanistan mission, but without the support of three leftists in the government.
6116	APW_ENG_20070221.1497.LDC2009T13	The decree awaits parliamentary approval.
