6189	APW_ENG_20070228.1118.LDC2009T13	Stocks fluctuated in a narrow range Wednesday, showing some signs of stability on a satisfactory gross domestic product report and a recovery on some markets in other countries.
6190	APW_ENG_20070228.1118.LDC2009T13	The major indexes opened higher and showed tepid resolve as the market sought to regain its footing a day after the Dow Jones industrials plunged 416 points amid growing concerns about slowing economies in the U.S. and China.
