6747	APW_ENG_20070328.1248.LDC2009T13	He told the House of Commons Wednesday that it was "now time to ratchet up the international and diplomatic pressure" on Tehran.
6748	APW_ENG_20070328.1248.LDC2009T13	That included the release by the British Defense Ministry Wednesday of GPS coordinates it said proved the 15 were in Iraqi waters when they were arrested -- about 1.7 nautical miles inside Iraqi waters on the Shatt al-Arab waterway.
6749	APW_ENG_20070328.1248.LDC2009T13	The ministry also said the Iranians had made inconsistent designations of the location where the incident occurred.
