6759	APW_ENG_20070402.0585.LDC2009T13	Ukraine's President Viktor Yushchenko convened parliamentary faction leaders on Monday to present a stark choice: stop trying to expand the majority coalition by poaching pro-presidential lawmakers or face the dissolution of parliament.
