6764	APW_ENG_20070402.0585.LDC2009T13	The stakes are high for the nation of 47 million and for Yushchenko, who is under enormous pressure from all sides.
6765	APW_ENG_20070402.0585.LDC2009T13	Yushchenko's former Orange Revolution allies held a major rally in the capital Saturday, urging him to dissolve parliament.
6766	APW_ENG_20070402.0585.LDC2009T13	Opposition leader Yulia Tymoshenko warned that protesters could stage a replay of Orange Revolution protests and "we won't disperse until the president signs the order" to disband the legislature.
