6975	APW_ENG_20070409.0043.LDC2009T13	About 4,500 NATO and 1,000 Afghan forces are in and around Helmand province as part of Operation Achilles.
6976	APW_ENG_20070409.0043.LDC2009T13	In the last several months, Taliban militants and foreign fighters have streamed into the province, according to U.S. and NATO officials.
