9118	APW_ENG_20070924.0079.LDC2009T13	Among the Detroit Three, the UAW picked GM as the lead company in negotiations and the union's potential strike target, so Ford Motor Co. and Chrysler LLC would likely match many of the terms of GM's agreement.
