10948	APW_ENG_20080502.1098.LDC2009T13	They say the battery should last for about 100,000 miles (160,000 kilometers) of driving.
10949	APW_ENG_20080502.1098.LDC2009T13	The company, formed in 2003, is named for inventor Nikola Tesla, an early pioneer in the field of electricity.
10950	APW_ENG_20080502.1098.LDC2009T13	The people buying its cars so far, said national sales manager Doreen Allen, are celebrities, early adopters, wealthy people and environmentalists.
