10983	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	Don't expect any promising teenagers to break into Sweden's squad for the European Championship.
10984	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	Lars Lagerback, the only coach ever to bring Sweden to five consecutive major championships, prefers experience over youth, and he will choose which players will head to Austria and Switzerland next month along those lines.
