11002	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	Anyone facing Sweden in a competitive match in the past few years could count on roughly the same formation: Zlatan Ibrahimovic spearheading the attack, Fredrik Ljungberg and Christian Wilhemsson foraying down the flanks, and workhorse Tobias Linderoth in a defensive midfield role.
11003	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	"We've been able to work all these years with a fundamental style of play.
