11009	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	That's no small feat for a country outside of Europe's traditional soccer elite.
11010	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	Still, many Swedes have criticized Lagerback for the nation's lack of success in the knockout stages.
11011	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	The Swedes lost to the Netherlands on penalties in Euro 2004 quarterfinals, and exited the last two World Cups in the round of 16 -- in extra time against Senegal in 2002 and after a 2-0 loss to host Germany in 2006.
11012	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	Lagerback doesn't think he could have done much differently.
11013	APW_ENG_20080511.0391.LDC2009T13	"Take Holland and Senegal.
