11373	APW_ENG_20080706.0397.LDC2009T13	He said two had died, while 12 were in critical condition.
11374	APW_ENG_20080706.0397.LDC2009T13	Violence levels have fallen in Pakistan since last year, but attacks still occur as resentment continues in some corners against the country's partnership with the U.S. in the war on terror.
11375	APW_ENG_20080706.0397.LDC2009T13	In June, a suicide car bomber killed at least six people near the Danish Embassy in Islamabad.
