11390	APW_ENG_20080706.0397.LDC2009T13	Kamal Shah, the interior ministry secretary, denied that the bombing was a result of poor security for the Red Mosque gathering, during which many attendees called for Islamic law and demanded the hanging of President Pervez Musharraf.
