13858	LTW_ENG_20070501.0152.LDC2009T13	Myers law firm argued at least twice against holding hearings in open court.
13859	LTW_ENG_20070501.0152.LDC2009T13	In one instance, an Anschutz lawyer specifically cited ``the problem'' of trying the case ``in the press.''
