13921	LTW_ENG_20070504.0120.LDC2009T13	A coalition of army reservists, students and relatives of war dead that organized the protest estimated turnout at between 150,000 and 200,000.
13922	LTW_ENG_20070504.0120.LDC2009T13	It was the largest rally against Olmert's government in the 13 months it has been in office.
13923	LTW_ENG_20070504.0120.LDC2009T13	``Ehud Olmert, you said you work for us,'' Meir Shalev, a renowned fiction writer, told the gathering.
