13926	LTW_ENG_20070504.0120.LDC2009T13	In 34 days of fighting, the army failed to crush the Hezbollah militia, stop it from firing rockets into Israel or free two captured soldiers.
13927	LTW_ENG_20070504.0120.LDC2009T13	While the panel did not call for resignations, its censure triggered an outcry among Israelis, who view the war as a defeat.
13928	LTW_ENG_20070504.0120.LDC2009T13	By a margin of 2 to 1 in most polls this week, they said they want Olmert and Peretz to resign.
