14763	LTW_ENG_20080111.0123.LDC2009T13	A subsequent investigation showed the U.S. ship was off course.
14764	LTW_ENG_20080111.0123.LDC2009T13	Pentagon spokesman Bryan Whitman said the new Iranian video does not refute the U.S. version.
14765	LTW_ENG_20080111.0123.LDC2009T13	"Simply choosing not to reveal the careless and reckless actions in this video does not change the facts from what took place," he said in an e-mail.
