16256	NYT_ENG_20070223.0174.LDC2009T13	The managers, mostly in their 30s, grew up in the area, went to college and, after a job or two, came to Padnos.
16257	NYT_ENG_20070223.0174.LDC2009T13	Al Tomes, director of operations and a 16-year Padnos employee, grew up in a one-stoplight town near here, where his parents operated a campground, he said.
