16481	NYT_ENG_20070310.0157.LDC2009T13	There is little about baseball that has appeared difficult for Ellsbury, who took some swings at Fenway Park with some other Cape Cod Leaguers in 2004, never imagining that a year later he'd be drafted on the first round by the Sox.
