16490	NYT_ENG_20070310.0157.LDC2009T13	"But the thing that impresses me about him is his efficiency of movement.
16491	NYT_ENG_20070310.0157.LDC2009T13	Some guys have a way of making the game look hard, a way of making it look difficult, but he keeps things pretty simple.
16492	NYT_ENG_20070310.0157.LDC2009T13	"There's not a lot of unnecessary movement.
