16827	NYT_ENG_20070408.0021.LDC2009T13	A counselor advised Rowin and his wife to visit with another family who took care of developmentally disabled children, just to get a taste of what their lives would become.
16828	NYT_ENG_20070408.0021.LDC2009T13	After the visit, one of Rowin's adopted kids asked him why they had visited with the children in wheelchairs.
