17479	NYT_ENG_20070619.0208.LDC2009T13	The appeal appeared to have little effect, though, as large groups of civilians mingled on the streets Tuesday and some students even sought to go to the local university.
17480	NYT_ENG_20070619.0208.LDC2009T13	The presence of so many civilians on an urban battlefield affords the operatives from al-Qaida another possible means to elude their American pursuers.
