17598	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	CAR BOMBS FAILED, BUT TERRORISTS ' DAMAGE IS WIDESPREAD
17599	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Cox News Service
17600	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	To those of a certain age - Generation Ex, let's say - "The Doctors' Plot" recalls the charge by Stalin that a cabal of physicians was scheming to poison Soviet political and military leaders.
17601	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Before the resulting round-up ran its course in early 1953, scores had been executed or exiled to the gulag.
17602	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Stalin died within months, all on his own and without the encouragement of any poison.
17603	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	The whole supposed plot had been a phony, as the new Kremlin leadership quickly conceded.
17604	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	The physicians arrested were almost all Jewish.
17605	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	The affair had been part of a broad campaign of anti-Semitism, which Stalin had ordered up.
17606	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Strip off the Soviet surface and, at bottom, you have an old fashioned Russian pogrom, with the gavel as the weapon of choice.
17607	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	(Stalin would have been in no danger even if the plot had been real.
17608	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Paranoid, he had long since quit medical doctors in favor of veterinarians.
17609	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	But a plot by wicked veterinarians would have been a tough sell even to a populace accustomed to being dutifully gulled.)
17610	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Now we have another doctors' plot, this one very real.
17611	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Six immigrant Muslim physicians are under arrest in Britain, another in Australia, dozens more have been questioned and Lord knows how many are being quietly investigated in other nations.
17612	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	The two car bombs in London, built to kill and to rip large numbers of innocents, in the manner for such enterprises, fizzled.
17613	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	Though it exploded, a hastily assembled third car bomb caused no injuries either, except to the two doctors aboard who rammed it into the Glasgow airport.
17614	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	But make no mistake.
17615	NYT_ENG_20070709.0030.LDC2009T13	There is wide collateral damage all the same, it's just not physical.
