17661	NYT_ENG_20070711.0048.LDC2009T13	At the moment, a man's ring is about $700 and a woman's ring is $360, campus officials said.
17662	NYT_ENG_20070711.0048.LDC2009T13	The Jarvis gift will be administered by a student group called Change, which started raising money to help their needy classmates buy rings in 2003.
