17839	NYT_ENG_20070804.0058.LDC2009T13	Her rollout to the public received rocky reviews from the political class, Republicans included.
17840	NYT_ENG_20070804.0058.LDC2009T13	A series of negative articles about her shopping habits, marital past and supposedly testy relations with campaign staff followed.
