18222	NYT_ENG_20071024.0170.LDC2009T13	But as Hasselbeck begins her 2-1/2 month maternity leave, the political landscape is shifting, as well.
18223	NYT_ENG_20071024.0170.LDC2009T13	America's most dangerous conservative - or so some liberals see it - is leaving TV for a while.
18224	NYT_ENG_20071024.0170.LDC2009T13	Hasselbeck, the apple-cheeked blonde with the football-player husband, consistently draws a brand of hatred from the left that Hillary Clinton generates from the right
