18598	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	in 2000 as a nonprofit, public-private organization in Tallahassee.
18599	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	Role: Oversees state's
18600	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	two dozen work force boards, including WorkNet Pinellas and the Tampa Bay WorkForce Alliance.
18601	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	Mission: To prepare
18602	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	workers for better jobs in growing industries via training programs, grants and counseling services.
18603	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	Size: About 25 employees.
