18607	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	Fast facts About Chris Hart IV Who he is: The new president and CEO of Workforce Florida Age: 39
18608	NYT_ENG_20071124.0092.LDC2009T13	Personal: Grew up in Tampa.
