18935	NYT_ENG_20071226.0223.LDC2009T13	That bacteria is similar to the type found in the common house cat, officials said.
18936	NYT_ENG_20071226.0223.LDC2009T13	The zoo was eerily quiet on the day after the tragedy.
18937	NYT_ENG_20071226.0223.LDC2009T13	The cafe where the attack victims were found was shuttered and still, and a dozen police officers gathered with zoo officials nearby, poring over maps and handing out equipment.
