19586	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	Cox News Service
19587	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	ATLANTA -- There's not a bit of bunting in sight.
19588	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	No rope line to hold back the rabid throngs.
