19621	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	"In my lifetime, we've not had an administration that has presented such a clear picture of why the current system is broken as the Bush administration, and that has changed the dynamics of the political system this year," Barr says.
19622	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	"The 'Ron Paul phenomenon,' so to speak, also illustrates that there is a significant group of folks out there who recognize that the Libertarian party does present to them very relevant issues of freedom."
