19624	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	What's not here - yet - are some of the more obvious outward trappings of a presidential run.
19625	NYT_ENG_20080425.0070.LDC2009T13	No "Straight Drawl Express" parked outside an Atlanta-based national campaign office, no paid full-time staff working inside.
