21486	XIN_ENG_20080215.0112.LDC2009T13	They also found no problems related to the purchase of raw materials or the production process.
21487	XIN_ENG_20080215.0112.LDC2009T13	"The plant is very clean and well-managed, and no abnormality has been detected," a Japanese investigator told the press after the inspection.
