21833	XIN_ENG_20080816.0437.LDC2009T13	By sports writers Bai Xu and Shen Nan
21834	XIN_ENG_20080816.0437.LDC2009T13	BEIJING, Aug. 16 (Xinhua) -- Superman Hancock not only exists in Hollywood movies.
21835	XIN_ENG_20080816.0437.LDC2009T13	The 19-year-old American young man has all the elements to be viewed a superman.
21836	XIN_ENG_20080816.0437.LDC2009T13	Full Name: Vincent Hancock.
